  <thing id="fPUAlternConscrip" name="Alternate Conscription" description="You&apos;ve broadened your methods of conscripting enemies.\n\n{b}Prerequisites:{/b} Conscription class feature.\n\n{b}Benefit:{/b} When you take this feat, you choose a method of conscription from a different set of highlord tenets. By expending your psionic focus as a free action, even if it isn&apos;t your turn, you may use the conscription ability of that tenet as if you were a highlord of that tenet for a round." compset="Feat" uniqueness="useronce">
