  <thing id="fPUBloodReveler" name="Blood Reveler" description="You delight in the pain inflicted by your lifeblood resonance.\n\n{b}Prerequisites:{/b} Lifeblood resonance class feature.\n\nBenefit: Once per round, when you deal damage to a creature with your lifeblood resonance, you may add your Charisma modifier to the damage of the ability and gain temporary hit points equal to the damage dealt by it. At 8th and 15th levels, you can apply this effect to an additional use of your lifeblood resonance each round." compset="Feat" uniqueness="useronce">
