  <thing id="cPUHilTenets" name="Highlord&apos;s Tenets" description="Many of a highlord&apos;s abilities draw power from his mere presence. How these abilities develop, however, are based on the tenets that he follows. At 1st level, a highlord chooses a set of tenets to follow." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Gain power from your chosen philosophy">
