  <thing id="cPUHighlordsGreed" name="Highlord&apos;s Greed" description="When the highlord uses the forceful tribute decree, the member of the collective targeted by the decree loses the effects of the designated tribute unless they make a Will save (DC 10 + 1/2 the highlord&apos;s class level + the highlord&apos;s Charisma modifier). The member of the collective regains the effects of the tribute if the forceful tribute decree ends.\n\nA highlord must know the forceful tribute decree to learn this greater decree." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Copied tribute benefits are lost by the original" uniqueness="useronce">
