  <thing id="cPUAbsoluteComman" name="Absolute Command" description="To use this decree, the highlord must expend 10 power points as a standard action. This decree acts like {i}Geth&apos;s mind control{/i}, targeting a member of his collective. Unlike that power, he can target the collective member regardless of line of sight, line of effect, or range. This decree ends if the creature leaves the highlord&apos;s collective.\n\nA highlord must know the highlord&apos;s command decree in order to learn this decree." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Use {i}mind control{/i} on a collective member" uniqueness="useronce">
