  <thing id="cPURestrainOrder" name="Restraining Order" description="Activating this decree is a free action, and it lasts for a number of rounds equal to the highlord&apos;s Charisma modifier (minimum 1 round). During this duration, as a swift action, the highlord can direct a member of the collective to halt. For 1 round, that collective member cannot willingly leave their space.\n\nUnlike most decrees, the collective member does not receive a save against this decree." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Force collective members to not move" uniqueness="useronce">
