  <thing id="cPUPersisConscrip" name="Persistent Conscription" description="As a swift action, the highlord can empower his collective&apos;s grasp for a number of rounds equal to his Charisma modifier (minimum 1 round). During this duration, whenever the highlord attempts to force creatures into his collective (such as through the Unwilling Participant feat), those creatures roll two d20s for their Will saves and take the lower result." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Make targets of Unwilling Participant roll twice and take lower" uniqueness="useronce">
