  <thing id="cPUMoveCommand" name="Movement Command" description="Activating this decree is a free action, and it lasts for a number of rounds equal to the highlord&apos;s Charisma modifier (minimum 1 round). During this duration, as a swift action, the highlord can direct a member of the collective to move. That collective member may immediately move up to their speed as a free action, even though it isn&apos;t their turn.\n\nThe highlord determines the direction of the movement. A creature unwilling to follow the highlord&apos;s orders can make a Will save to resist the orders and forgo actions granted by the highlord." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Command collective members to move during your turrn" uniqueness="useronce">
