  <thing id="cPUFalter" name="Falter" description="As a swift action, the highlord chooses a member of the collective to suffer one of the following penalties for a number of rounds equal to the highlord&apos;s Charisma modifier (minimum 1 round):\n\n• –2 penalty on attack rolls, and double that penalty on skill checks.\n• –1 penalty to armor class and on saving throws.\n• –1 penalty to the save DCs of the creature&apos;s abilities (including spells and powers).\n\nWhen the highlord has this decree active, as a swift action, he can inflict an additional penalty to a member of the collective for the same duration as the original decree. Successive uses of this ability for the same penalty do not stack; however, the highlord can afflict a creature with multiple penalties at once, if he uses this decree on a target multiple times.\n\nAt 7th level and every six highlord levels thereafter, these penalties increase by 1. This decree is not a mind-affecting effect." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Inflict penalties on collective members" uniqueness="useronce">
