  <thing id="cPUBearMyBurden" name="Bear My Burden" description="Whenever the highlord suffers from any of the following conditions, he may activate this decree as an immediate action, even if the condition would prevent him from taking an immediate action.\n\nBleed, Blinded, Confused, Cowering, Dazed, Dazzled, Deafened, Energy Drained, Exhausted, Fascinated, Fatigued, Frightened, Nauseated, Panicked, Paralyzed, Petrified, Shaken, Sickened, Staggered, Stunned\n\nThe highlord designates another member of the collective who has at least half the Hit Dice of the highlord and is not immune to the condition. This member of the collective begins to suffer the effects of the condition instead of the highlord. If the member of the collective succeeds at resisting the decree, the highlord suffers the condition as normal.\n\nHowever, if they accept the exchange or fail to resist it, the highlord is no longer affected by the condition and the member of the collective suffers it in the highlord&apos;s place for its remaining duration. The duration of the decree is identical to the duration of the condition. If they leave the collective or the highlord ends this decree, they are freed from the condition, and the highlord suffers the condition for the remainder of its duration.\n\nA highlord must be 7th level or higher to choose this decree." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Transfer negative conditions to collective members" uniqueness="useronce">
