  <thing id="cPUHilLifebTithe" name="Lifeblood Tithe" description="A despot&apos;s lifeblood resonance allows him to freely drain away the life of those under his rule. Once per round as a free action, the despot can deal his lifeblood resonance damage to a chosen member of his collective within close range (25 feet + 5 feet per two class levels). The despot is healed for half the damage that they suffer, not including bonus damage from other sources. At 8th level, the despot can deal this damage to up to two members of the collective at once. At 15th level, the despot can deal this damage to up to three members of the collective at once." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Damage members of  your collective to heal">
